description:
Our next meetup will be in April. It's another virtual meetup. Join us on zoom at 7 pm. You'll get the link when you RSVP.

We're delighted to have three fantastic talk this month from:

** Nerando Johnson: Level 1.5 Full Stack Developer (Javascript and Ruby) ** ⚡️talk

The importance of ReadMes and documentation.

** David Corking: Raise your git ambitions ** ⚡️talk

I encourage you to push your git UI to the limit, and enjoy git more.

** Mike Rogers: Seeding Data In Ruby On Rails **

A good seeds.rb, helps every app grow. Let's go through the techniques for seeding so you'll actually want to do it.
* * *

Slack

If you have any questions or suggestions, please join us on Slack. Go to https://bathruby-for-slackers.herokuapp.com and find us in the #south-west-ruby channel.
title: South West Ruby #33 (ONLINE)
